<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>throw one’s weight • throw one’s weight about</xh5><p> <i>throw one’s weight</i>—(also: swing one’s weight) use one’s influence and personal power to get smth. done, etc.: I was prepared to <u>throw my weight</u> in Cung’s favor. But he mistrusted me and rejected my council.</p><p> <i>throw one’s weight about</i>—(also: throw one’s weight around) aggressively assert oneself: She was in here the other day, <u>throwing her weight about</u> as if she was Hedy Lamarr and Katharine Hepburn rolled into one.</p> </entry>
